user.biography: A Place Like No Other™. Home to 71 rides, including 18 roller coasters, Cedar Point Shores Waterpark and more.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Cedar Point on September 19, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and outdoors.

node.text:
Today is a great day for trick-or-treating! 🍬 

Kids 12 & under can visit TEN Trick-or-Treat stations for fun and sweet surprises! Pick up your card near Kiddy Kingdom's entrance during the Tricks & Treats Fall Fest at #HalloWeeeknds!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Cedar Point on September 18, 2021. May be an image of outdoors.

node.text:
Today is the first day of Tricks and Treats Fall Fest at #HalloWeekends for the 2021 season! 🎃 We're so excited to welcome you to the park today! Family-friendly activities will be going on until 7p. 🍬

Haunted houses will open at 6p and outdoor scare zones will open at 8p. 👻

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Cedar Point on September 17, 2021.

node.text:
That face you make when you're only HOURS away from the opening of #HalloWeekends! 😂 

The park opens at 6p with Early Entry starting at 5p! See you soon! 🎃👻👹

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Cedar Point on September 16, 2021. May be a black-and-white image.

node.text: Show of hands ✋ who is ready for the start of HalloWeekends TOMORROW??? 🎃

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Cedar Point on September 15, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says '××× RIES FORRAL NOTIC ESF STIC FOOD & BEVERAGE POSITIONS $20/hr'.

node.text:
We have GREAT Food & Beverage positions starting at $20 per hour! 🤑 Server positions are available as well for $10 an hour PLUS tips! 🤑😍 

Flexible scheduling, great teamwork, FUN incentives and more await you when you apply for a job at cedarpoint.com/jobs!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Cedar Point on September 15, 2021. May be an image of outdoors.

node.text:
Snoopy is looking “gourd-geous” today and is almost ready for this weekend! 

See him in all his pumpkin glory at The HalloWeekends Great Pumpkin Spectacular! 🎃

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Cedar Point on September 10, 2021. May be an image of nature.

node.text:
It's been a long week, and we've missed you! We'll see you tomorrow when we reopen our gates for the weekend! 

See our hours for Sept. and Oct. here: bit.ly/3dm2WEx

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Cedar Point on September 08, 2021. May be an image of 8 people, people standing and indoor.

node.text:
There's still time to apply for great fall jobs. 🎃 

Starting at $20/hour, we have openings all over the park. We need costume stitchers, performers, techs and that's just with our Live Entertainment Team!

There's something for everyone! Apply now at: cedarpoint.com/jobs

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Cedar Point on September 07, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and outdoors.

node.text:
Wicked Twister wasn't the only retiree yesterday... 

From changing coaster train wheels, to reassembling the cabins on Giant Wheel each year, Frank did it all! Congratulations on nearly 40 years of service to Cedar Point! Enjoy your retirement. 😄

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Cedar Point on September 06, 2021. May be an image of 3 people, people standing and outdoors.

node.text: Today is TRUCE DAY at Forbidden Frontier on Adventure Island! 🎉 Visit as the residents end the season with an EPIC finale around 6:00 p.m. Drama and conflict are coming to the island... and that's jus’ the beginning! 😳😁

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Cedar Point on September 06, 2021. May be an image of outdoors and text that says 'A PASS LIKE NO OTHER 2022 GOLD PASS T Cedar Point GOLDPASS GOLD PASS 2022'.

node.text:
Only a few hours left to get a 2022 Gold Pass for ONLY $99! The price goes up at midnight! 
cedarpoint.com/pass
